---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
    title="Home | Cascading Labs"
    description="Cascading Labs is building the future of data and algorithms, starting with web data and finance."
>
    <h1 class="text-xl font-medium mb-10 tracking-tight" style="color: var(--cl-text);">
        Cascading Labs
    </h1>

    <p class="mb-6 font-light" style="color: var(--cl-text-muted);">
        We are building the future of data and algorithms.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-6 font-light" style="color: var(--cl-text-muted);">
        We aren't fully sure what that means yet, but we have the following
        assumptions:
    </p>

    <ul class="mb-6 pl-5 list-disc" style="color: var(--cl-text-muted); --tw-marker-color: var(--cl-text-marker);">
        <li class="mb-2 pl-2 font-light">Black-box AI is universally dumb.</li>
        <li class="mb-2 pl-2 font-light">
            Knowledge is the impetus of action.
        </li>
        <li class="mb-2 pl-2 font-light">Causality is too complicated.</li>
        <li class="mb-2 pl-2 font-light">
            Fact checkers are necessarily biased.
        </li>
        <li class="mb-2 pl-2 font-light">
            Knowledge is a virus, and it spreads.
        </li>
    </ul>

    <div class="mt-14 flex gap-2 -ml-2">
        <a
            href="https://github.com/CascadingLabs"
            class="cl-link"
            aria-label="Visit Cascading Labs on GitHub"
        >
            GitHub
        </a>
        <a
            href="/yosoi"
            class="cl-link"
        >
            Yosoi
        </a>
    </div>
</Layout>

